Assignment Name : RedBus.in 

In this assignment, we are entering basic details like ( source, destination, and date ) and we are clicking on the submit button.
As soon as you enter all the details, All the bus details will be displayed and we have to select the type and select the seats and click
on proceed to book button. After clicking on the button, we have to enter the passenger basics details and click on proceed to pay button.


So there are 2 ways to run the script through eclipse:

1) Click on testng.xml file > Click on Run As  > TestNG Suite

   In testng.xml, we have to provide the class name that needs to be run
   
2) You can directly through the class
    
    Go to class file under src/ test / java 
    Right click on test class.java > Click on Run As > TestNG Test


